rows.label: qev300151_MSG0001
rows.name:
Oh, forget it. No one is REALLY going to turn up with
4,000 units of miranium![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300151_MSG0002
rows.name:
I tried to make the Mission Control post sound all
impressive, but I'm sure everybody's got better things
to do than supply us...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300151_SEL0021
rows.name: Hold on to your miranium for now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300151_MSG0004
rows.name:
Sweet crispy cheese! You've single-handedly kept
Meredith & Co. up and running![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300151_MSG0005
rows.name:
Wow. I guess the moral of this story is to never get
your hopes up...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300151_MSG0006
rows.name:
Guess I'm not the only one who's really hurting for
4,000 units of miranium.[ST:wait ]
